OOC
===

Usage: ooc <message>     - Send an out-of-character message
       ooc on            - Subscribe to OOC chat
       ooc off           - Unsubscribe from OOC chat
       ooc history [N]   - View last N messages (default 20)

Out-of-character chat channel for discussions that aren't part of the
game world (real-life topics, game mechanics questions, etc.).

Examples:
  ooc Anyone know how to join the mages guild?
  ooc brb dinner
  ooc history

Alternative: Use 'history ooc [N]' to view OOC history.

See also: chat, channels, history
